    <h1>Review Velocity</h1>
    <p class="description">The rate at which a business earns new reviews over time — measured in reviews per week or month. A growing ranking factor: businesses with <strong>consistent velocity rank 2-3 positions higher</strong> in the local pack than those with stalled review profiles.</p>
